
    [6/13/14] Max Payne 3 PC Title Update v130 Notes


>>>Removal of GameSpy features, which have been replaced by Social Club services.
    
>>>Store purchases removed from the non-Steam versions of the game. Please note that you can still buy Max Payne 3 DLC redemption codes from 
   Steam or other digital retailers, and redeem them in the disc version of the game to access additional content.
    
>>>Voice chat improvements to push-to-talk and voice activation thresholds.

>>>If you are having any problems updating to the latest version of Max Payne 3 automatically when the game is booted, please use the manual
   patch download.
